Sentencas: An anodic cermet of NiCu alloy and gadolinia doped ceria has been investigated for CH4 electro-oxidation in IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Performance and life-time behaviour of NiCu-CGO anodes for the direct electro-oxidation of methane in IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Polarization curves have been recorded in the temperature range from 650 to 800 degrees C. A maximum power density of 320 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C has been obtained in the presence of dry methane in an electrolyte-supported cell.
Titulo: Performance and life-time behaviour of NiCu-CGO anodes for the direct electro-oxidation of methane in IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The electrochemical behaviour during 1300 h operation in dry methane and in the presence of redox-cycles has been investigated at 750 degrees C; variation of the electrochemical properties during these experiments have been interpreted in terms of anode morphology modifications.
Titulo: Performance and life-time behaviour of NiCu-CGO anodes for the direct electro-oxidation of methane in IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The methane cracking process at the anode catalyst has been investigated by analysing the oxidative stripping of deposited carbon species.
Titulo: Performance and life-time behaviour of NiCu-CGO anodes for the direct electro-oxidation of methane in IT-SOFCs
